  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Battery replacement in a smartphone: TransformationEvent for the swap,",
    "plus an ObjectEvent inspecting the removed battery prior to WEEE disposal.",
    "",
    "Repair KDEs (repairType / repairDescription / technician / warrantyStatus /",
    "repairCost) are observation-specific to THIS repair and therefore ride at",
    "event level (EPCIS 2.0 §12.3), NOT in ilmd.",
    "ilmd on OBSERVE events is forbidden by EPCIS 2.0 §7.3.8 — the second event",
    "used to have one; those fields are now at event level.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: dpp=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,electronics=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/electronics/",
    "See: extensions/common/core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
